name: Execution 1D
description:
Live from the SkreedCo Arena in Scrambler City!!

The Prisoner's UV Blinder is initiated with electroshock pulses into the eye sockets, creating a low traversal point to the brain. This causes convulsions and an erosion of flesh, for which the Prisoner is outfitted with a boiling suit on the exposed epidermis. After the Prisoner has been executed, they will be divided into Nutrition Cubes for the citizens.
